+Search for a product (by name, barcode, SKU, etc.).
+
+Fetch data from multiple “markets” (retailers or e-commerce platforms) for that product: price, availability, specs, shipping, etc.
+
+Compare those results in a clean UI (table, list, charts) so users can easily pick the best deal.
+
+Track prices over time (price history) to help users decide when to buy.
